headline: USA Compression Q2 Earnings Beat Estimates, Revenues Rise Y/Y
summary: USAC expects adjusted EBITDA of $590-$610 million and distributable cash flow between $350 million and $370 million for 2025.

headline: Delek Q2 Loss Narrower Than Expected, Revenues Miss Estimates
summary: DK expects total crude throughput in the range of 291,000-306,000 bpd and total throughput in the band of 302,000-317,000 bpd for third-quarter 2025.
